OL,3,CRace to keep blast furnaces on at
OL,4,CBritish Steel's Scunthorpe plant
OL,6,FThe government and British Steel are
OL,7,Fworking to secure the raw materials
OL,8,Fneeded to keep two blast furnaces on,
OL,9,Fin a race against time to avoid a
OL,10,Fpermanent shutdown of Britain's last
OL,11,Fprimary steelmaking plant.
OL,13,FOfficials from the Department for
OL,14,FBusiness and Trade (DBT), along with
OL,15,FBritish Steel staff, will spend Monday
OL,16,Fworking to bring nearby raw materials
OL,17,Fonto the site, as well as ensuring
OL,18,Fstaff continue to be paid, the
OL,19,Fdepartment said.
