OL,3,CRace to keep blast furnaces on at
OL,4,CBritish Steel's Scunthorpe plant
OL,6,FWithout raw materials, such as coking
OL,7,Fcoal and iron ore, the blast furnaces
OL,8,Fwill cool and will eventually be
OL,9,Fturned off and can never be turned
OL,10,Fback on, meaning the end of
OL,11,Fsteelmaking at the Scunthorpe plant.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News on Sunday,
OL,14,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,15,Fsaid he was "confident" they would
OL,16,Fkeep the plant working but would not
OL,17,Fdisclose any details.
