OL,3,CRace to keep blast furnaces on at
OL,4,CBritish Steel's Scunthorpe plant
OL,6,FParliament sat in a rare weekend
OL,7,Frecall on Saturday to pass emergency
OL,8,Flegislation, giving the government the
OL,9,Fpowers to prevent the Chinese owner of
OL,10,Fthe plant, Jingye, from closing blast
OL,11,Ffurnaces at the site.
OL,13,FThe business secretary could not
OL,14,Fguarantee this would not happen but
OL,15,Fsaid taking over the plant had given
OL,16,Fthe government "a chance" to save it.
OL,18,FReynolds said: "When I said
OL,19,Fsteelmaking has a future in the UK, I
OL,20,Fmeant it.
