OL,3,CRace to keep blast furnaces on at
OL,4,CBritish Steel's Scunthorpe plant
OL,6,F"That's why we've passed these new
OL,7,Fpowers to save British Steel at
OL,8,FScunthorpe, and that's why my team are
OL,9,Falready hard at work on the ground to
OL,10,Fkeep jobs going and furnaces burning."
OL,12,FJingye, British Steel's Chinese
OL,13,Fowners, had not only stopped ordering
OL,14,Fraw materials but had begun selling
OL,15,Foff existing supplies, sparking
OL,16,Fconcerns the plant could close within
OL,17,Fdays.
