OL,3,CRace to keep blast furnaces on at
OL,4,CBritish Steel's Scunthorpe plant
OL,6,FDozens of businesses, including Tata
OL,7,Fand Rainham Steel, have rallied to
OL,8,Fhelp British Steel with offers of
OL,9,Fmanagerial support and raw materials
OL,10,Ffollowing the government's takeover.
OL,12,FThe offers of support from other
OL,13,Fbusinesses also mean that British
OL,14,FSteel is reassessing its options and
OL,15,Fcould reverse Jingye's decision to
OL,16,Ftake one of the blast furnaces
OL,17,Ftemporarily offline on Monday using a
OL,18,Fdangerous procedure known as a
OL,19,F"salamander tap".
