OL,3,CRace to keep blast furnaces on at
OL,4,CBritish Steel's Scunthorpe plant
OL,6,FThe cost of modernising the site could
OL,7,Frun into the billions as ministers
OL,8,Fremain hopeful a private investor can
OL,9,Fbe found for British Steel.
OL,11,FOver the weekend, the business
OL,12,Fsecretary admitted that full
OL,13,Fnationalisation remained the most
OL,14,Flikely option.
OL,16,FHe said: "Steel is vital for our
OL,17,Fnational security and our ambitious
OL,18,Fplans for the housing, infrastructure
OL,19,Fand manufacturing sectors in the UK.
