OL,6,F"We will set out a long-term plan to
OL,7,Fco-invest with the private sector to
OL,8,Fensure steel in the UK has a bright
OL,9,Fand sustainable future."
OL,11,FThe Conservatives have accused the
OL,12,FLabour government of acting "too late"
OL,13,Fand implementing a "botched
OL,14,Fnationalisation" after ignoring
OL,15,Fwarnings about the risk to British
OL,16,FSteel.
